data.title: Titusville PA funeral home and cremation
data.meta_description: All Obituaries - Gordon B Garrett Funeral offers a variety of funeral services, from traditional funerals to competitively priced cremations, serving Titusville, PA and the surrounding communities. We also offer funeral pre-planning and carry a wide selection of caskets, vaults, urns and burial containers.
data.meta_site_name: All Obituaries | Gordon B Garrett Funeral | Titusville PA funeral home and cremation
data.text: You are welcome to call us any time of the day, any day of the week, for immediate assistance. Or, visit our funeral home in person at your convenience.
